No fucking way.

782
00:42:28.090 --> 00:42:30.300
What? What is it?

783
00:42:30.300 --> 00:42:31.880
This thing's protected.

784
00:42:31.880 --> 00:42:34.680
Well. hack it. Isn't. like. cybersecurity what you do?

785
00:42:34.680 --> 00:42:38.050
Uh. this isn't ordinary security. or 2ⁿᵈ or 3ʳᵈ level.

786
00:42:38.060 --> 00:42:40.640
My aunt acted like she couldn't even set up a modem.

787
00:42:40.640 --> 00:42:44.140
But this has national-intelligence level
security that I can't even get around.

788
00:42:44.140 --> 00:42:46.520
[KEYBOARD CLACKING]

789
00:42:52.700 --> 00:42:54.110
This thing's locked.

790
00:42:54.110 --> 00:42:55.990
[ROSE SIGHING]
- So you can't see anything?

791
00:42:55.990 --> 00:43:00.040
Well. there's just a folder with a name on it. but it can't be opened.

792
00:43:05.580 --> 00:43:06.420
No way.

793
00:43:07.540 --> 00:43:08.750
[ ♪ OMINOUS MUSIC ♪ ]

794
00:43:10.550 --> 00:43:12.630
What? What?
- PETER: Holy shit. No. no.

795
00:43:12.630 --> 00:43:16.130
2781 is the number of the metro train I was on.

796
00:43:16.140 --> 00:43:17.640
The one that got bombed. Rose.

797
00:43:17.640 --> 00:43:20.180
What the hell were your aunt and uncle doing investigating that?

798
00:43:20.180 --> 00:43:23.980
Well. I don't know until I can crack it.
which I can't do without serious hardware.

799
00:43:26.690 --> 00:43:28.060
Hey. who are you calling?

800
00:43:28.060 --> 00:43:30.110
Diane Farr. She can get you the hardware you need.

801
00:43:30.110 --> 00:43:31.360
ROSE: Hey. slow down.

802
00:43:31.360 --> 00:43:33.150
We don't know who we can trust.

803
00:43:33.150 --> 00:43:35.240
What if she tracks the call and sends someone here?

804
00:43:35.240 --> 00:43:38.160
She can't trace this call. I'm calling the Night Action line.

805
00:43:41.120 --> 00:43:42.040
DIANE: This is Farr.

806
00:43:42.040 --> 00:43:44.660
MAN: <i>This is Night Action. I have Peter Sutherland for you.</i>

807
00:43:44.660 --> 00:43:45.710
Put him through.

808
00:43:46.420 --> 00:43:48.370
Where are you? Where's Rose?
- PETER: <i>We're safe.</i>

809
00:43:48.380 --> 00:43:50.420
Did you figure out who pulled her protection?

810
00:43:50.420 --> 00:43:52.840
Hawkins called off her Secret Service detail.

811
00:43:52.840 --> 00:43:53.920
PETER: <i>You're sure?</i>

812
00:43:54.420 --> 00:43:57.130
The order was issued from a computer in his office.

813
00:43:57.130 --> 00:43:58.380
He confess?

814
00:43:58.390 --> 00:43:59.390
No.

815
00:43:59.390 --> 00:44:02.720
Looks like whoever his accomplices were
made sure he couldn't tell us anything.

816
00:44:04.270 --> 00:44:06.640
A farmer found him in a field in Maryland.

817
00:44:07.230 --> 00:44:08.190
Murdered.

818
00:44:09.060 --> 00:44:11.560
Somebody killed the deputy director of the FBI?

819
00:44:11.570 --> 00:44:13.320
Shot him in the back 6x.

820
00:44:14.110 --> 00:44:14.940
6x?

821
00:44:14.940 --> 00:44:17.150
PETER: It's not safe for you and Rose out there.

822
00:44:17.150 --> 00:44:18.280
What are you doing?

823
00:44:21.200 --> 00:44:22.700
We found a hard drive.

824
00:44:22.700 --> 00:44:24.990
<i>Rose's aunt and uncle were hiding it.</i>

825
00:44:25.000 --> 00:44:27.000
We can't get into it. It's encrypted.

826
00:44:27.620 --> 00:44:29.870
I think it has something to do with the metro bombing.

827
00:44:29.880 --> 00:44:33.500
Peter. come in already. Just bring Rose and come on in.

828
00:44:33.500 --> 00:44:36.380
<i>If Hawkins was behind this. whoever his accomplices were...</i>

829
00:44:36.380 --> 00:44:38.130
they'll kill anyone they deem a threat...

830
00:44:38.130 --> 00:44:40.390
and you and Rose are definitely a threat now.

831
00:44:41.430 --> 00:44:42.850
<i>Peter. this is an order.</i>

832
00:44:42.850 --> 00:44:44.220
Come in right now...

833
00:44:44.220 --> 00:44:46.600
and bring Rose and the hard drive with you.

834
00:44:52.110 --> 00:44:54.020
[ ♪ SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC SWELLING ♪ ]

835
00:44:54.080 --> 00:48:12.360
１

836
00:44:54.080 --> 00:48:12.360
０

837
00:44:54.080 --> 00:48:12.360
６

838
00:44:54.080 --> 00:48:12.360
５

839
00:44:54.080 --> 00:48:12.360
７

840
00:44:57.080 --> 00:48:18.360
Ｔ Ｈ Ｅ
NIGHT AGENT

841
00:44:56.150 --> 00:44:57.900
